description:
Cross-Platform AI Benchmark

Geekbench AI is a cross-platform AI benchmark that uses real-world machine learning tasks to evaluate AI workload performance. Geekbench AI measures your CPU, GPU, and NPU to determine whether your device is ready for today's and tomorrow's cutting-edge machine learning applications.
- Upgrade to ONNX Runtime 1.20 on Windows
- Upgrade to OpenVINO 2024.5.0 on Windows and Linux
- Upgrade to Samsung ENN 3.1.10 on Android
- Upgrade to Qualcomm QNN 2.28.2.241116 on Android
- Requantize ONNX models
  - Update how ONNX models are quantized to improve both performance and accuracy, improving quantized workload scores on Windows systems.
- Improve support for Snapdragon 8 Elite devices
